BanAxe - Ban AND have fun!

Right click the bad bay to create a lightning which will hit him and, after 2 seconds, will ban him.

Commands:
/banaxe enable to enable the banaxe
/banaxe disable to disable the banaxe
/banaxe item ID to choose your ban item
/banaxe global ID reason to globally ban a user (needs mcbans)
/banaxe help shows all commands ingame

Permissions:
BanAxe.Use


Hail the axe!